survey_response.review_text: I have visited the doctor for various injuries since 2013. Listens to the patient, soft spoken and provides prudent advice.

Good he told me in detail about the problem and the solution... 

Since I supposed to travel the next day to some other city there he told me how to take treatment in that city hospital.. 

But I have canceled my travel and continued treatment with him .. 

I am totally satisfied..

Dr. Sharath Chandra is a very experienced orthopedic who recommends what is actually required in the situation.He never recommended unnecessary tests, treatments or medications like many other  orthopedics. Iam going there for past 8 years & always got the rite treatment. I also recommended him to my friends & family and everyone gave an excellent feedback.

I was recommended by a friend of mine and I was glad I considered. His explanations are simple *** ********* ** ********** There was no glamorization of the problem or solution. This is the very reason I don't mind traveling from malleshwaram to jayanagar to consult with him.
The doctor is excellent; he doesn't talk much, but his work is smart, perhaps due to his vast experience.

The doctor was very clear with the issue. He kept unnecessary expenditure to a minimum by only recommending tests that were necessary and after explaining why it was needed. His explanation of the issue was very clear and the resolution was optimal
Superb analysis. Doctor will not unnecessarily recommend for surgery. Listens patiently and does what is needed. Recommends good exercise and natural healing.

When I come to the hospital I have very pain in my Nick and shoulder that time doctor examined my physical condition and friendly explained above the problem and given good treatment, thanks to Dr.Sharath Chandra.
Nice experience with doctor and explanation of issue and remedies given by doctor will help us a lot.

Clearly explained the problem and available solutions so that l could choose the best option.
Treatment was to my satisfaction.
